snippet.title: Sega Mega Drive: Global Gladiators
snippet.description:
http://www.Insert-Disk.com proudly presents "Global Gladiators" for the Sega Mega Drive/Genesis.

Stage 1.

One of McDonald's video games. You play as two eco warrior children that must rid the world of pollution. I'm really not a fan of this one but it was a hit back in the early 90's.
